# Portela-Hub Rules

## 🚫 SUPABASE IS DISCONTINUED
- Do NOT use `@supabase/supabase-js`.
- Do NOT suggest Supabase Edge Functions.
- Do NOT use Supabase Auth.

## 🐘 NATIVE POSTGRESQL ONLY
- All database operations must use native SQL via MCP (`vps_james_sql`).
- Architecture is exclusively native PostgreSQL.

## 📁 REPOSITORY SCOPE
- These rules apply strictly to the Portela project (IP 69.62.103.45).
